name: Late photographer 5
description:
A simple and easy beauty dynamic jigsaw puzzle and relaxing music can make you have a good mood

Each girl has a small plot

The way of the game: click one puzzle with the mouse, and then click another puzzle.

The positions of the two puzzles will change with each other.

Complete the puzzle by observing the pattern of the puzzle and exchanging the position of the puzzle.

After the puzzle is completed, there will be dynamic picture display.
